room_title: Escape room "Spell Struck!" by The Escape Artist in Seattle
room_address: 4517 California Ave SW Suite B, Seattle, WA 98116
room_description:
Legend tells of a coven within Seattle that gathers every decade to perform a spell and extend their mortality. They lure helpless travelers deep within the woods, as sacrifices for their black magic. You and your group of friends happen to be lost in the woods, just in time for this supposed ritual 
…but that’s just a legend, right?
